title: Marco Ferreri - La Grande Bouffe - 1973
description:
<a href="http://imdb.com/title/tt0070130/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://imdb.com/title/tt0070130/</a>

A.K.A. Blow Out (but I've never heard anybody use that title)

The first time I saw it I thought I'd lost my appetite.  The second time, dragging some friends, I was insatiable after the film was over.

A cast to die for.  Marcello Mastoianni, Michel Piccoli, Ugo Tognazzi, Philipe Noiret. I'd die to have been part of the cast. Even as a vegetarian, I'd have loved to have come with the meat wagon.

Uncompressed PAL VIDEO_TS files with culinary extras.

Just try to enjoy it more than me.

Thanks to the original uploader
